= Legal & Compliance =

FactHarbor's legal foundations, financial governance, and public commitments.

== 1. Legal Foundations ==

* **[[Legal Framework>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Legal Framework.WebHome]]**
Our organisational form (Swiss Association), intellectual property, and data protection strategy.

* **[[Open Source Model and Licensing>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Open Source Model and Licensing.WebHome]]**
Our commitment to open source (AGPL/MIT) and how it protects our mission.

* **[[Contributor License Agreement (CLA)>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.CLA.WebHome]]**
How we manage copyright and license grants for contributions to the project.

== 2. Public Policies ==

The formal rules that protect our users and define our commitments to the public.

* **[[Privacy Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Privacy-Policy]]**
How we process and protect user data under Swiss and international law.

* **[[Transparency Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Transparency-Policy]]**
Our commitment to auditability, open data, and open decision-making.

* **[[Terms of Service>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Terms-of-Service]]**
The legal agreement for interacting with the FactHarbor platform.

* **[[Security Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Security-Policy]]**
Principles for system integrity, vulnerability reporting, and incident response.

== 3. Financial Governance ==

How we manage resources to ensure long-term independence and survival.

* **[[Finance and Compliance>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Finance and Compliance.WebHome]]**
Our non-profit budgeting process, internal controls, and reporting.

* **[[Large Donations Policy>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Large Donations Policy.WebHome]]**
The rules protecting our independence from donor influence (the 20% rule).

* **[[Reimbursable Expenses>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Reimbursable Expenses.WebHome]]**
Guidelines for expense management and our public transparency ledger.
